    <div id="whatif" style="list-style-type:none;">
      <img src="/images/front_page/whatif.png"/>
      <ul class="advantages">
        <li>I actually looked forward to exercising?</li>
        <li>my jeans started to fit better?</li>
        <li>"boot camp" didn't mean yelling?</li>
        <li>I found a new group of friends?</li>
        <li>I could improve my community?</li>
      </ul>
