    <div class="clear"></div>
    <p class="big_red" style="text-align:left;">FitWit works for <strong><em>EVERY</em></strong> fitness level!</p>

    <p class="bigGray" style="text-align:justify;">We add up everything cool about teams &#8211; camaraderie, support,
      fun &#8211; And then we subtract everything you hate about sports &#8211; ultra-egos, smelly teammates, 3 hour
      practices &#8211; and we mash it up into what we call FitWit. Serious fitness for people who don't take themselves
      too seriously.</p>

    <p class="bigGray" style="text-align:justify;">Think measurable workouts with cool stuff &#8211; kettlebells,
      sandbags, medicine balls and think certified trainers coaching you to personal greatness! And guess what? There's
      a cherry on top&#8230;</p>

    <p class="bigGray" style="text-align:justify;">ONE FitWit camp gives ONE Atlanta child ONE free week of FitWit. It's
      simple &#8211; Get Fit, Give Fit, Live Fit.</p>

    <p class="bigGray" style="margin:0 auto 15px auto;text-align:left;">
      Need more
      details?  <%= link_to "Click here for the FitWit Difference.", {:controller => "fitness_camp_info", :action => "the_fitwit_difference"}, :style => "color:#535353;" %>
    </p>

